Package com.tomzhu.hash

a group of hash table structures by different hashing method.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CuckooHashTable<K,V>
    a simple cuckoo hashing table implementation.
    ExtensibleHashTable<K,V>
    a simple extensible hash table implementation.
    HashTableByLinearProbing<K,V>
    a simple hash table implementation by linear probing where h(i) = i.
    HashTableByQuadraticProbing<K,V>
    a simple quadratic probing hash table implementation where h(i) = i^2.
    HashTableBySeparateChain<K,V>
    A simple hash table implementation using separate Chain.
    HopscotchHashTable<K,V>
    a simple hopscotch hash table implementation.
    PerfectHashingTable<K,V>
    a simple perfect hashing table implementation.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    CuckooHashTable.HashTableType
    a cuckoo hash table type holder.

Package com.tomzhu.hash Description

a group of hash table structures by different hashing method. including CuckooHashTable, HopscotchHashTable, etc.
Since:
1.7
Author:
tomzhu
